{"type": "article", "id": 26625, "title": "Gap 销售额再度下滑，以及，Brixton 夏装和帽子不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-10T11:03:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14443, "name": "男士护肤"}, {"id": 27424, "name": "一季度销售额"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 26947, "name": "日式"}, {"id": 27425, "name": "女性企业家"}, {"id": 22712, "name": "奖学金"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2882, "name": "Tory Burch"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 19052, "name": "Rag & Bone"}, {"id": 27426, "name": "Biotherm"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021113347nfGSjX4YdMq8hEN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Old-Navy-Banana-Republic-weigh-on-Gap-as-sales-slip-yet-again,690971.html#.VzExGoQrJQY\"><b>Gap 销售额再度下滑</b></a>｜Gap 集团近日公布一季度财报，已经是第五个季度销售额直线下滑，Banana Republic 门店可比销售额降低了 11%，Old Navy 则是 6%，Gap 下滑了 3%。Gap 集团净销售额减少了 6% 至 34.4 亿美元，低于预期的 35.4 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Rag-Bone-hires-Lydia-Forstmann-as-new-Chief-Commercial-Officer,690883.html#.VzEyeoQrJQY\"><b>Rag &amp; Bone 任用新首席商业官</b></a>｜Rag &amp; Bone 周一宣布 Lydia Forstmann 成为公司首席商业官（CCO），这是公司首次开设这一职位，新的职位上，Lydia 将领导公司批发、零售、推销及商业开发，直接向 Rag &amp; Bone 的 CEO David Neville 和 Marcus Wainwright 报告。 Lydia  此前在 Tory Burch 担任过多种行政职位长达八年，最后的职位为美国批发及全球旅游零售高级副总裁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/David-Beckham-to-develop-new-skin-care-line-for-men,690642.html#.VzE1IYQrJQY\"><b>贝克汉姆将推出男士护肤系列</b></a>｜大卫·贝克汉姆近日成为护肤品牌碧欧泉男士（Biotherm Homme）代言人，宣布将推出合作男士护肤系列产品线。不过这并不是他首次涉足美妆系列，2005 年与 Coty  合作发布首支香水 Instinct。而与碧欧泉的合作预计在 2017 年上市。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/tory-burch-names-10-women-entrepreneurs-fellowship-program-10426789/\"><b> Tory Burch 进行女性企业家培养计划</b></a>｜Tory Burch 基金会挑选 10 位女性企业家参加其为其一年的培养计划，一年中将为这些参与者提供教育、指导和交流机会，包括 1 万美元的商业教育资金。从超过 500 位的候选者中挑选 30 位入围决赛，由公众在网络上投票帮助决定最终 10 位入选者。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/human-resources/givenchy-dior-parfums-alain-lorenzo-to-step-down-from-lvmh-fragrance-brands-10426723/\"><b>LVMH 香水品牌总裁兼 CEO 辞职</b></a>｜LVMH 香水品牌总裁兼 CEO Alain Lorenzo 近日宣布因个人原因辞职，7 月生效。Alain 同时还是 Givenchy 香水长期总裁。Christian Dior 香水欧洲区总经理 Romain Spitzer 将接替其职位，他毕业于巴黎高等商学院，过去曾为娇兰（Guerlain）、Jean Paul Gaultier 香水、Yves Saint Lauren 等品牌工作。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Gucci 与  Net-A-Porter 的联名系列，<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/5/9/11641092/gucci-net-a-porter-capsule-collection#6471091\">更多细节图</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111317KpWMnqJUAlCbTPsB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111318AXc2DbvzBNOJlu6G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111318L85atZDBIsno1SFi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111319Z0p3iF9wu8LAgzqY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111319TjS5GMAHwlab8XQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111320KAPExJgyB1luWD4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111320I73905pO8gRzWkLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111321sQAGkz97D5CpSg0l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113215xCriI1ln94VAMqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">加州品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/brixton-summer-2016-collection\">Brixton 推出最新夏日系列</a>，除了适用于街头、沙滩的 T 恤、泳衣和滑板裤以外，还有遮挡阳光的男女草帽、软昵帽等：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111322cl0I9szOZA6ME2hD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111322M64KknuOAlc7wrNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113233KZXEIH2C45oP0AU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113230OCVe9iMBok4cJPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111324KTPHw0z47nLue3V5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111325rouKXCMi2Hm5ZwjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111325rfsoHY4zQxjvhNFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111326e4ohsbDRSP3vX9TA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://bagaholicboy.com/2016/04/louis-vuitton-pre-fall-2016-monogram-canvas-collection/\">Louis Vuitton 早秋系列包袋</a>，经典的 monogram 花纹增添了些新意：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111326qfPMQBL9JIt5T6yA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113276woM1lRScpFBIy8W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111327K67NBbUWcDAi0zYO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">如果你钟情于日式服装，可以看看日本男装品牌  Sasquatchfabrix 为庆祝日本知名百货 Beams 成立 40 周年而推出的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/sasquatchfabrix-oriental-skate-collection\">“东方滑板（Oriental Skate）”胶囊系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111328b1z0c4oOeP5lpfWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111329AUXa45yfe61nSDsu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111329vhyJCgPe7H5tZXAF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111330InB4hjTe0XrzfxL5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111331zeBvnLgRMdr0FfsC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/jimmy-choo-pre-fall-2016-shop/\">Jimmy Choo 2016 早秋系列</a>高跟鞋，融合动感及优雅：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111331v7FfNVwqLi43EZKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111332RVNBUSptcLwPie61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111332pEiPkm9WhKvIoD6N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111332lBMsNCSQ6G9tTWo0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113336TWxprAqzkGiBOum.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111333RW6dlSrscHP49VzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}